critical_positive: I think the fact that I listened and paid close attention to what the other person had to say. It really helped deepen the conversation. I also asked plenty of questions. I tried to limit dominating the conversation with my voice. I believe that listening and paying attention provided insight into my conversation partner.
critical_negative: At the beginning, I tried to see if the other person would ask questions. I noticed that they really didn't. critical_positive: What worked well was that we were both generally outgoing people. We worked off of what each other said to keep the conversation going once it got started. critical_negative: There's really not much that didn't go well.
